指用来说明、解释某种理论或看法而引用的例证。

word_group.brief_definition: 好榜样；良好范例；良好示例
经典例子；经典案例；经典实例

bilingual.source: Can you give an example of this?

bilingual.target: 蒙特梭利学校就是一个例子。

bilingual.source: Here is an example of a food chain at sea.
bilingual.target: 这是一个海洋食物链的例子。

bilingual.source: It is an example of a traditional performance art.
bilingual.target: 它是传统表演艺术的一个例子。

bilingual.source: What is one example of the English way of life?
bilingual.target: 英国生活方式的一个例子是什么？

bilingual.source: Perhaps the best example is shown by UNESCO.
bilingual.target: 也许最好的例子是联合国教科文组织展示的。

bilingual.source: The Beijing Olympic Forest Park is a good example.
bilingual.target: 北京奥林匹克森林公园是一个很好的例子。

list.abstract: Example（1983年6月20日-），原名Elliot Gleave，出生于英国伦敦，英国男歌手。 2007年9月，发行专辑《What We Made》。2011年，发行单曲《Unorthodox》。2012年11月，发行合唱单曲《We'll Be Coming Back》。2014年3月，发行专辑《Kids Again （Remixes）》。2018年2月，发行单曲《The Answer（James Hype Remix）》。2019年3月，发行合唱专辑《Icons Only （Explicit）》。2023年1月，发行专辑《Смотри》。

Example原名Elliot Gleave，生于伦敦，生日是1983年6月20日，是一名英伦歌手、饶舌歌手。艺名Example的来历是由于他的本名缩写e.g.在拉丁文中是exempli gratia的缩写，也就是英文中的for example。Example的音乐类型大概可以归为Eleotro,hip hop,grime和dubstep。 2013年，Example与澳大利亚模特、演员Erin McNaught喜结连理。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't follow. Let me give you an example.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没听明白。我给你举个例子吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Not necessarily. This is a classic example of Munchausen's Trilemma.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不一定非得有，这是Munchausen三难推理的典型例子。

yingyinNormal.en: I like to back people who want to succeed. Take yourself as an example.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我愿意支持渴望成功的人，你自己就是个例子。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, may I ask for one example? Yeah, it's, you know there's... No, you may not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请你举出一个例子。就是有，例如…反正你不是。

yingyinNormal.en: That was actually a poorly chosen example, as it had nothing to do with me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个例子其实举得很烂，因为那跟我一点关系也没有。

yingyinNormal.en: A perfect example is chicken chow mein. And it's one of my favourite take-outs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 鸡肉炒面就是一个完美的例子，这也是我最爱的外卖食品之一。

yingyinNormal.en: The knife, for example, is the last thing you learn. Okay? Okay. Position.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拿刀来举个例子，刀是你要学习的最后一件武器，明白吗？好的。找位置。

yingyinNormal.en: What if I came into your office and I started...? I can't think of an example. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么？试想一下我到你的办公室，然后开始...？我想不出一个合适的例子。

yingyinNormal.en: But as this is an example when Jeff illustrates these all equivalent examples financially, it is just how theses framed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是杰夫举的一个例子用金融的角度来阐述这些经营模式。

yingyinNormal.en: Gangnam Style is another great example of how that just took over and became huge worldwide world pop phenomenon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 江南style是另一个刚刚成功的好例子，它刚刚成为世界范围的流行现象。

yingyinNormal.en: Look at Korean pop, look at K-pop for example. Korea is an export-based economy and they are outward looking and they must be outward looking.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看韩语流行音乐的例子，韩国是一个基于出口的经济，他们向外看，而且他们必须向外看。

yingyinNormal.en: PS: An awesome down-to-earth example of stable orbits are the hyperbolic funnels that you often see at museums or in shopping malls.
yingyinNormal.zh: 备注：一个非常棒且实际关于稳定轨道的例子是我们经常能够在博物馆或是购物中心看见的大型"漏斗"。

yingyinNormal.en: A lot of what America perceives as Asian is very foreign. Yao Ming was kind of a quintessential example of that. He's from China, he's from the east. And he's coming to our shores
yingyinNormal.zh: 在许多美国人眼里亚洲人是十分遥远和陌生的，姚明是一个典型的例子，他来自中国，他来自东方，到达我们的海岸。

yingyinNormal.en: So here is for example the situation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 通过以上情况给出的例证。

yingyinNormal.en: Your self-knowledge is an example to us all.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的自知之明值得我们所有人学习。

yingyinNormal.en: Look to your elder, people. Let him be an example.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们看看这个老家伙，他就是你们的榜样。

yingyinNormal.en: For example Oculus Reparo. That's better, isn't it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如说欧卡拉斯雷培洛，很快就修好了。

yingyinNormal.en: With certain obvious exceptions. Suicide, for example.
yingyinNormal.zh: 显然也有例外，比如说，自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: It was nice of her to show us playing dumb with an example.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她人真好，还亲自示范怎么装傻逼。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm using that as an example. We're ready. I'll be right there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只是以此为例。准备好了。马上就到。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: something such as an object, a fact or a situation that shows, explains or supports what you say

examination_example.sentence: A calm, rule-following child might respond better to a different sort of parenting than, for <highlight>example</highlight>, a younger sibling.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一个冷静、遵守规则的孩子，例如，一个弟弟妹妹，可能比其他孩子对不同类型的养育方式反应更好。

examination_example.sentence: For <highlight>example</highlight>, heavier women are less likely to develop calcium deficiency than thin women.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，体重较重的女性比瘦的女性更不容易出现缺钙。

examination_example.sentence: About a quarter of all Italian immigrants, for <highlight>example</highlight>, eventually returned to Italy for good.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，大约四分之一的意大利移民最终永远回到了意大利。

sense_info_list.en: a representative form or pattern; something to be imitated

examination_example.sentence: Set an <highlight>example</highlight> for future deals.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为未来的交易树立榜样。

examination_example.sentence: Set an <highlight>example</highlight> for other journals.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为其他期刊树立榜样。

sense_info_list.en: a printed or written problem or exercise designed to illustrate a rule

examination_example.sentence: In Estonia and Ireland, for <highlight>example</highlight>, the number of death has fallen by about two thirds since the late 1990s.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，自20世纪90年代末以来，爱沙尼亚和爱尔兰的死亡人数下降了约三分之二。

examination_example.sentence: In certain US states, for <highlight>example</highlight>, these rights are treated similarly to property rights, and are transferable to a person's heirs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，在美国的某些州，这些权利与财产权类似，可以转让给个人的继承人。

examination_example.sentence: Marconi's <highlight>example</highlight> demonstrates that theoretical concepts and experiments complement each other in making progress in science and technology.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Marconi的例子表明，理论概念和实验在科技进步中是相辅相成的。

examination_example.sentence: Finally, relevant regulatory authorities should also strictly monitor the behavior of pop stars and ensure that they set good <highlight>examples</highlight> for teenagers.

examination_example.sentence: Many of them are following the <highlight>example</highlight> set by Thailand.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们中的许多人都在以泰国为榜样。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation:
同for instance。来举例说明某一论点或情况，一般只举同类人或物中的“一个”为例。
例：For example, you’re not supposed to put your bread on your plate.
比如，你不应该把你的而包放在盘子里。

用来列举事物时，一般列举同类人或事物中的几个例子。
例：Cartoon characters such as Mickey Mouse and Snoopy are still popular.
动画片中的角色，比如米老鼠和史努比，现在仍然很受欢迎。
